(21, 'Blue Cheese', 'Romain Lx', '  A small taste of France with this typical blue cheese mould style.\r\n\r\n2 shapeburst fill + 1 inverted polygons (with geometry generator) if you need to find a nice cheesy colour.\r\nMaybe inadequate for datasets with large number of polygons', '../styles/resources/5f2b028244e4f1.91634423.xml', '../styles/images/5f2b028244e595.02806186.png', 'lacxrx', NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
